These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, pear, apple, tomato
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, 7up, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, documentary, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, dubstep, rock
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, dannemann, siglo, pall-mall
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, quad-bike, train
 1. the pall-mall-smoker is the fan of dubstep##1
 2. the person drinking juice is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is the dannemann-smoker##1
 6. the person eating pear is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 8. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking 7up is the person eating tomato##1
10. the person driving the boat is the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating pear##1
13. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
14. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of d&b##1
15. the person watching action movies is the person eating pear##1
16. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person eating apple##1
17. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4        |
| Food         | tomato    | cranberry      | apple | pear        |
| Beverage           | 7up | juice     | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | documentary | mystery   | action         |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | rock        | dubstep   | d&b            |
| Cigar           | vegafina       | dannemann  | pall-mall    | siglo         |
| Transport     | boat       | jet-ski     | train     | quad-bike      |

