.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, soy-milk
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, whist, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, martial-arts, spy
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, chinese, canadian, french
4 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, mauve, green, white
 1. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
 3. the canadian is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 4. the person playing domino is the french##1
 5. the person playing domino is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the chinese is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the person who likes green is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 9. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes white##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching spy movies##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
12. the person watching action movies is the person who likes white##1
13. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left or far right##3
14. the owner of the mouse is the person watching spy movies##1
15. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
16. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
17. the canadian is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
18. the canadian is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice      | cola         | lemonade | soy-milk    |
