.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-3::.
House: cape-cod, farmhouse, gothic-revival, victorian
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, peas, pomegranate, pumpkin
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, librarian, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, house, jazz
4 different pets are kept: fish, lizard, snake, turtle
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, may, january
 1. the security-guard is the fan of blues##1
 2. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the security-guard##1
 3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 4. the person eating peas is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of disco is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 6. the librarian is the person eating cucumber##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the lizard and the fan of jazz##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is the owner of the snake##1
 9. the victorian house is between the person eating pomegranate and the freelancer##2
10. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
12. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |     4      |
| House      | farmhouse       | cape-cod          | victorian   | gothic-revival    |
| Food          | cucumber   | pomegranate    | pumpkin    | peas       |
| Job           | librarian  | security-guard | lawyer     | freelancer |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | blues      | jazz  | house   |
| Pet           | lizard     | turtle         | fish       | snake      |
| Birthday         | august | february           | january | may     |

